Mg_rox_shotgun_pushcircle
-----------------------------
This map is a newer version of the orginal mg_pushcircle (by Shur!k)

The map is way more smoother than orginal
There are no buyzones, on spawn u get a m3 and a knife. 12 auto-shotguns are in the map.

40 spawnpoints. 20 each team.
